               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><svg viewbox=\"0 0 800 200\"><rect width=\"800\" height=\"180\" fill=\"#0f172a\"/><text x=\"400\" y=\"30\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#e2e8f0\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\">Representação da emissão do átomo de Hidrogênio</text> <g transform=\"translate(50, 80)\"><line x1=\"0\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"700\" y2=\"70\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"0\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\">1</text><text x=\"80\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\">90</text><text x=\"115\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\">130</text><text x=\"165\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\">365</text><text x=\"518\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\">700</text><text x=\"590\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\">820</text><text x=\"350\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\">Comprimento de onda (nm)</text><text x=\"100\" y=\"0\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#fbbf24\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\">Lyman</text><text x=\"200\" y=\"0\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#34d399\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\">Balmer</text><text x=\"600\" y=\"0\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c084fc\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\">Paschen</text><rect x=\"175\" y=\"15\" width=\"350\" height=\"40\" fill=\"url(#visibleGradient)\" opacity=\"0.3\"/> <text x=\"350\" y=\"0\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#e2e8f0\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\">Luz visível</text><line x1=\"91\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"91\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#fbbf24\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><line x1=\"93\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"93\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#fbbf24\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><line x1=\"102\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"102\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#fbbf24\" stroke-width=\"1\"/> <line x1=\"175\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"175\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"2.0\"/><line x1=\"180\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"180\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"3.0\"/><line x1=\"185\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"185\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"3.0\"/><line x1=\"190\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"3.0\"/><line x1=\"200\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"200\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/> <line x1=\"224\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"224\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"274\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"274\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"455\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"455\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/> <line x1=\"600\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"600\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#c084fc\" stroke-width=\"3.0\"/> <line x1=\"605\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"605\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#c084fc\" stroke-width=\"3.0\"/><line x1=\"609\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"609\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#c084fc\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"612\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"612\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#c084fc\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"620\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#c084fc\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"630\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"630\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#c084fc\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"650\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"650\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#c084fc\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"675\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"675\" y2=\"55\" stroke=\"#c084fc\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><defs><linearGradient id=\"visibleGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0%\"><stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"#8b5cf6\"/><stop offset=\"20%\" stop-color=\"#3b82f6\"/><stop offset=\"40%\" stop-color=\"#22c55e\"/><stop offset=\"60%\" stop-color=\"#eab308\"/><stop offset=\"80%\" stop-color=\"#f97316\"/><stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#ef4444\"/></linearGradient></defs></svg></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Gráfico 2</b>: Espectro do átomo de hidrogênio.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "O espectro é formado por linhas verticais espaçadas de acordo com as medições realizadas.",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "A falta de linhas que cobrem toda a imagem, como visto no **Gráfico 2**, levou Bohr a aprimorar o modelo atômico proposto por Rutherford.\n\nDe acordo com Bohr, os elétrons não podem mover-se livremente ao redor do núcleo; em vez disso, movem-se apenas em órbitas bem definidas.\n\nEles se deslocam para órbitas maiores ao receber energia (luz) e retornam para órbitas menores ao emitir luz (<htcite0>).\n\nO **Gráfico 3** mostra o modelo de Bohr para o átomo de hidrogênio. Nesta representação, o núcleo foi pintado de amarelo para diferenciar as órbitas possíveis do elétron.",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "c72c0fc7-eb03-46ab-ac97-16e6e849e4af",
